thread.title: Ryan Delany

author: Ryan Delany
title: Ryan Delany
text: I ordered a set of 8 coil over packs and installed them this past weekend and I'm very happy with the experience. Ordering was easy, shipping was quick, Araparts provided timely communication the entire time, the parts were well packaged, they installed just like OEM parts, and so far they are working great. The only thing I was Araparts did was include 2 dielectric grease packs instead of 1. I wouldn't hesitate to order parts again from Araparts.
